MIXXX Controller mapping for Hercules DJ Controller Instinct
@author: mich@softwareschneiderei.ch

http://mixxx.org/



Description of Mappings

Hot Cue
=======
(off -> click MODE)
1,2 : Select/Store Hotcue 1,2
3,4 : Delete Hotcue 1,2




